summary.label:
This is online version of SCP Foundation database Wiki, for comfortable reading.

If you don't know what is SCP Foundation: this is wiki project what contain a lot very interesting information about anomaly, sci-fi, objects, places and creatures. All information is not real, but can be used for inspiration, and for create books, games, movies...

Features:
- Online reading SCP Foundation objects and Tales;
- Search;
- Favorite option what allow you to save favorite page;
- Open Random Object;
- Landscape and portrait orientations support;
- White and black theme;
- Update new objects;
- 2 reading modes what allow you get data from SCP or nn5n Foundation;
- 3D Touch support;
- Face ID/Touch ID Sign In;

Support online reading SCP Foundation on 12 languages:
- Chinese;
- English;
- German;
- French;
- Japanese;
- Italian;
- Korean;
- Polish;
- Portuguese;
- Spanish;
